Vcs-Browser: http://linux.thai.net/websvn/wsvn/software.thaifonts-arundina/?sc=0
Homepage: http://linux.thai.net/projects/thaifonts-arundina
Standards-Version: 3.8.1

Package: ttf-thai-arundina
Architecture: all
Depends: defoma (>= 0.7.0), x-ttcidfont-conf, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Thai DejaVu-compatible fonts in TrueType format
 This package provides Arundina fonts for Thai language in TrueType format.
 The fonts are designed to be compatible with Bitstream Vera or DejaVu fonts.
 Serif, sans-serif and monospace type faces are included.

Package: t1-thai-arundina
Architecture: all
Depends: defoma (>= 0.7.0), xfonts-utils (>= 1:1.0.0-4), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Thai DejaVu-compatible fonts in Type1 format
 This package provides Arundina fonts for Thai language in Type1 format.
 The fonts are designed to be compatible with Bitstream Vera or DejaVu fonts.
 Serif, sans-serif and monospace type faces are included.
